msgid ""
"Copy-paste a text blurb with data on the object, and KStars will try to "
"guess the contents of the fields from the text. The result is just a guess, "
"so please verify the coordinates and the other information."
msgstr ""
"Skopírujte a vložte text s údajmi o objekte a KStars sa pokusí odhadnuť "
"obsah polí z textu. Výsledok je iba odhad, preto overte súradnice a ostatné "
"informácie."

