#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (AlignmentPlot, targetPlot)
#: ekos/align/pushtoassistant.ui:47
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Description</span></"
"p><p>This assistant gives users of manual mounts (dobsons etc.) support "
"finding their targets using a finder scope equipped with a camera.</"
"p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Preparation</span></p><p>Open EKOS, "
"create a profile with the camera of your choice, the Telescope Simulator as "
"mount and add your finder scope as new telescope.</p><p><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Usage</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: "
"0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Start EKOS</li><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Position your mount as close as possible to "
"your target</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Select "
"your target in the target finder and press the &quot;Select target&quot; "
"button</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Press the &quot;"
"Solve position&quot; button. This captures a frame through your finder scope "
"and solves the image against the star catalogs of KStars.</li><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">As soon as plate solving succeeds, the "
"distance to the target is displayed. Arrows show the directions how to "
"correct your mount position.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">Move your mount in the indicated position and repeat solving.</"
"li></ul><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Hints</span></p><ul style="
"\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -"
"qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">If you "
"press the &quot;Repeat&quot; button, capturing and plate solving will be "
"repeated after the configured delay.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">If plate solving fails, check if the focal length of your "
"finder scope is correctly configured and your telescope is roughly pointing "
"to the target that you have selected.</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Popis</span></"
"p><p>Tento pomocník poskytuje používateľom manuálnych montáží (dobsonov "
"atď.) podporu pri hľadaní cieľov pomocou hľadáčika vybaveného kamerou.</"
"p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Príprava</span></p><p>Otvorte EKOS, "
"vytvorte profil s kamerou podľa vášho výberu, simulátorom ďalekohľadu ako "
"montáž a pridajte váš hľadáčik ako nový ďalekohľad.</p><p><span style=\" "
"font-weight:600;\">Použitie</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-"
"bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Spustite EKOS</li><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Umiestnite montáž čo "
"najbližšie k cieľu</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\">Vyberte cieľ vo vyhľadávači cieľov a stlačte tlačidlo &quot;Vybrať "
"cieľ&quot;</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Stlačte "
"tlačidlo &quot;Riešiť polohu&quot;. Toto nasníma rámec cez váš hľadáčik a "
"rieši snímku oproti hviezdicovým katalógom KStars.</li><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Akonáhle riešenie platničky uspeje, zobrazí sa "
"vzdialenosť k cieľu. Šípky ukazujú smery korekcie polohy montáže.</li><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Presuňte montáž na "
"vyznačenú polohu a opakujte riešenie.</li></ul><p><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Tipy</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: "
"0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" "
"margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Ak stlačíte tlačidlo &quot;"
"Opakovať&quot;, snímanie a riešenie platničky sa zopakuje po "
"nakonfigurovanom oneskorení.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">Ak riešenie platničky zlyhá, skontrolujte, či je ohnisková "
