#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QComboBox, focusCFZAlgorithm)
#: ekos/focus/cfz.ui:501
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Select the Critical Focus Zone (CFZ) algorithm:</p><ul "
"style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: "
"0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Classic</span>: Uses the formula, CFZ = "
"4.88 t λ f<span style=\" vertical-align:super;\">2.</span>.  Set tolerance, "
"t=1 for the basic formula. Some have suggested t=1/3 empirically.</li></"
"ul><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Wavefront: </span>Uses the "
"formula, CFZ = 4 t λ f<span style=\" vertical-align:super;\">2</span>.  "
"Formula derived from wavefront aberration theory. Some have suggested t=1/3 "
"or even t=1/10.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; "
"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Gold: </"
"span>Uses the formula, CFZ = 0.00225 √τ θ f<span style=\" vertical-align:"
"super;\">2. </span>A.  See http://www.goldastro.com/goldfocus/ncfz.php for "
"more details.</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Výber algoritmu kritickej zaostrovacej zóny (CFZ):</"
"p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Klasický</span>: Používa "
"vzorec CFZ = 4,88 t λ f<span style=\" vertical-align:super;\">2.</span> "
"Nastavte toleranciu t=1 pre základný vzorec. Niektorí empiricky navrhli "
"t=1/3.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-"
"left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Vlnová "
"plocha: </span>Používa vzorec CFZ = 4 t λ f<span style=\" vertical-align:"
"super;\">2</span>. Vzorec odvodený z teórie aberácie vlnovej plochy. "
"Niektorí navrhli t=1/3 alebo dokonca t=1/10.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-"
"top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-"
"indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span "
"style=\" font-weight:600;\">Gold: </span>Používa vzorec CFZ = 0,00225 √τ θ "
"f<span style=\" vertical-align:super;\">2.</span> A. Podrobnosti pozri na "
"http://www.goldastro.com/goldfocus/ncfz.php.</li></ul></body></html>"

