#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusCurveFitLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:357
#, kde-format
msgid "Curve Fit:"
msgstr "Prispôsobenie krivky:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QComboBox, focusAlgorithm)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:373
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Select focus process algorithm:</p><ul style=\"margin-"
"top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-"
"indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span "
"style=\" font-weight:600;\">Iterative</span>: Moves focuser by discreet "
"steps initially decided by the step size. Once a curve slope is calculated,  "
"further step sizes are calculated to reach optimal solution. The algorithm "
"stops when the measured HFR is within percentage Tolerance of the minimum "
"HFR recorded in the procedure.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Polynomial</span>: Starts "
"with iterative method.  Upon crossing to the other side of the V-Curve,  "
"polynomial fitting coefficients along with possible minimum solution are "
"calculated. This algorithm can be faster than purely iterative approach "
"given a good data set.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Linear</span>: Samples focus inward in "
"a regular fashion, using 2 passes.  The algorithm can be slow, but it is "
"more resilient to backlash.  Start with the focuser positioned near good "
"focus.  Set Initial Step Size and Max Travel for the desired sampling "
"interval and range around start focus position.  Tolerance should be around "
"5%.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Linear 1 Pass</span>: Starts like <span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Linear</span> but after completing the 1st pass, instead of "
"doing a 2nd pass,  moves straight to the minimum HFR value calculated.  Use "
"Curve Fit of Hyperbola or Parabola.</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Vyberte algoritmus procesu zaostrovania:</p><ul style="
"\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -"
"qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
"left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span "
"style=\" font-weight:600;\">Iteratívny</span>: Pohybuje zaostrovačom "
"diskrétnymi krokmi pôvodne rozhodnutými veľkosťou kroku. Po výpočte sklonu "
"krivky sa vypočítajú ďalšie veľkosti krokov pre dosiahnutie optimálneho "
"riešenia. Algoritmus sa zastaví, keď namerané HFR je v rámci percentuálnej "
"Tolerancie minimálneho HFR zaznamenaného v procedúre.</li><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;"
"\">Polynomiálny</span>: Začína iteratívnou metódou. Po prechode na druhú "
"stranu V-krivky sa vypočítajú koeficienty polynomiálneho prispôsobenia spolu "
"s možným minimálnym riešením. Tento algoritmus môže byť rýchlejší ako čisto "
"iteratívny prístup pri dobrej sade dát.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Lineárny</span>: "
"Vzorkuje zaostrovanie dovnútra pravidelným spôsobom, pomocou 2 priechodov. "
"Algoritmus môže byť pomalý, ale je odolnejší voči vôli. Začnite so "
"zaostrovačom nastaveným blízko dobrého zaostrovania. Nastavte Počiatočnú "
"veľkosť kroku a Max. pohyb pre požadovaný interval vzorkovania a rozsah "
"okolo počiatočnej polohy zaostrovania. Tolerancia by mala byť okolo 5 %.</"
"li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Lineárny 1 prechod</span>: Začína ako <span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Lineárny</span>, ale po dokončení 1. prechodu namiesto "
"vykonania 2. prechodu prejde priamo na vypočítanú minimálnu hodnotu HFR. "
"Použite Prispôsobenie krivky Hyperbola alebo Parabola.</li></ul></body></"
"html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, focusAlgorithm)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:380
#, kde-format
msgid "Iterative"
msgstr "Iteratívne"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, focusAlgorithm)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:385
#, kde-format
msgid "Polynomial"
msgstr "Polynomiálny"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, focusAlgorithm)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, kcfg_RAGuidePulseAlgorithm)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, kcfg_DECGuidePulseAlgorithm)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, Normalization)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:390 ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:106
#: ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:142 fitsviewer/livestacking.ui:1702
#, kde-format
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "Lineárny"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, focusAlgorithm)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:395
#, kde-format
msgid "Linear 1 Pass"
msgstr "Lineárny 1 prechod"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, focusRefineCurveFit)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:403
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Check to run an outlier pass when all datapoints have "
"been taken. The pass uses Peirce's Criteria for outlier threshold detection. "
"If there are outliers, these are removed and curve fitting rerun. If the R² "
"is improved by the process then this new dataset is used and outliers "
"highlighted on the v-curve. </p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Zaškrtnite pre spustenie prechodu odľahlých hodnôt po "
"zozbieraní všetkých datových bodov. Prechod využíva Peirceho kritériá pre "
"detekciu prahu odľahlých hodnôt. Ak existujú odľahlé hodnoty, tieto sa "
"odstránia a prispôsobenie krivky sa znovu spustí. Ak sa proces zlepší R², "
"použije sa táto nová sada dát a odľahlé hodnoty sa zvýraznia na v-krivke. </"
"p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, focusRefineCurveFit)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:406
#, kde-format
msgid "Refine Curve Fit"
msgstr "Spresniť prispôsobenie krivky"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusR2LimitLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:419
#, kde-format
msgid "R² Limit:"
msgstr "Limit R²:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusHFRFramesCountLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:432
#, kde-format
msgid "Average HFR Check:"
msgstr "Kontrola priemerného HFR:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QSpinBox, focusHFRFramesCount)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:445
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Number of frames to capture when running in-sequence HFR Check. If using "
"Linear 1 Pass, the point of optimum focus will also capture this number of "
"frames."
msgstr ""
"Počet rámcov na snímanie pri spustení kontroly HFR v sekvencii. Pri použití "
"Linear 1 Pass sa na bod optimálneho zaostrovania tiež nasníma tento počet "
"rámcov."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QSpinBox, focusGaussianKernelSize)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:490
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The gaussian blur kernel size. Used for blurring the "
"image before for instance the Bahtinov edge detection.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Posun v minútach na spustenie záznamu pred časom "
"kulminácie.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusGaussianKernelSizeLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:515
#, kde-format
msgid "Kernel size:"
msgstr "Veľkosť štvorca:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusGaussianSigmaLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:531
#, kde-format
msgid "Sigma:"
msgstr "Sigma:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusMultiRowAverageLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:547
#, kde-format
msgid "Num. of rows:"
msgstr "Počet riadkov:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusThreshold)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:566
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><body><p>Increase to restrict the centroid to bright cores. Decrease "
"to enclose fuzzy stars.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><body><p>Zvyšte hodnotu, aby ste obmedzili centroid na jasné jadrá. "
"Znížte ju, aby ste zahrnuli rozmazané hviezdy.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QSpinBox, focusMultiRowAverage)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:594
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Combine this number of rows in the Bahtinov max "
"average calculation. Change this value might help to match the Bahtinov "
"lines on the star pattern more accurate.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Skombinovať tento počet riadkov pri výpočte "
"maximálneho priemeru Bahtinovho vzoru. Zmena tejto hodnoty môže pomôcť "
"presnejšie priradiť Bahtinove čiary k hviezdicovému vzoru.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusGaussianSigma)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:619
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The gaussian blur sigma value. Used for blurring the "
"image before for instance the Bahtinov edge detection.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Posun v minútach na spustenie záznamu pred časom "
"kulminácie.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusTolerance)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:663
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Decrease value to narrow optimal focus point solution radius. Increase to "
"expand solution radius"
msgstr ""
"Znížte hodnotu na zúženie polomeru riešenia optimálneho bodu zaostrovania. "
"Zvýšte pre rozšírenie polomeru riešenia"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, focusDenoise)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:691
#, kde-format
msgid "Check to denoise the image before further processing."
msgstr "Zaškrtnite pre odrušovanie snímky pred ďalším spracovaním."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, focusDenoise)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:694
#, kde-format
msgid "Denoise"
msgstr "Odrušiť"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QGroupBox, focusDonut)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:709
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Check to enable Donut Busting functionality. Use on "
"telescopes with a central obstruction that create donut shaped stars when "
"defocused.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Zaškrtnite pre povolenie funkcie Donut Busting. "
"Použite na ďalekohľadoch s centrálnou clonou, ktoré vytvárajú hviezdy v "
"tvare šišky pri defokuse.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, focusDonut)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:712
#, kde-format
msgid "Donut Buster"
msgstr "Hviezdokopa Vážky"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:736
#, kde-format
msgid "Time Dilation x:"
msgstr "Časová dilatácia x:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusTimeDilation)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:755
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>The furthest datapoints have their exposure times "
"increased by this factor. The in focus datapoint exposure is not increased. "
"Intermediate points have their exposures scaled appropriately.</p><p>Set to "
"1 to disable this option.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Najvzdialenejšie datové body majú svoje časy expozície "
"zvýšené týmto faktorom. Expozícia datového bodu v ohnisku sa nezvyšuje. "
"Stredné body majú svoje expozície primerane škálované.</p><p>Nastavte na 1 "
"pre zakázanie tejto možnosti.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_2)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:783
#, kde-format
msgid "Outlier Rejection:"
msgstr "Odmietanie odľahlých hodnôt:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusOutlierRejection)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:802
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>How aggressively to apply Outlier Rejection. Higher "
"values reject more outliers.</p><p>Refine Curve Fit must be set for this "
"option to be active.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Ako agresívne aplikovať odmietnutie odľahlých hodnôt. "
"Vyššie hodnoty odmietajú viac odľahlých hodnôt.</p><p>Spresniť prispôsobenie "
"krivky musí byť nastavené pre aktiváciu tejto možnosti.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QGroupBox, focusScanStartPos)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:827
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Check to scan for a start position. The algorithm will "
"look for a minimum data point using Num Datapoints.</p></body></html>"
msgstr "<html><head/><body><p>Preemptívne hodiny vypnutia</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QGroupBox, focusScanStartPos)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:830
#, kde-format
msgid "Scan for Start Position"
msgstr "Skenovať počiatočnú polohu"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_4)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:857
#, kde-format
msgid "Initial Step Size x:"
msgstr "Počiatočná veľkosť kroku x:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QDoubleSpinBox, focusScanStepSizeFactor)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:873
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Scan for Start Position uses a step size = Initial Step Size multiplied by "
"Initial Step Size x."
msgstr ""
"Skenovanie pre štartovaciu pozíciu používa veľkosť kroku = Počiatočná "
"veľkosť kroku vynásobená Počiatočnou veľkosťou kroku x."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, focusScanAlwaysOn)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:898
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Check to always run Scan for Start Position, uncheck to only run after a "
"failed Autofocus."
msgstr ""
"Zaškrtnite pre vždy spustenie Skenovania pre štartovaciu pozíciu, zrušte "
"zaškrtnutie pre spustenie iba po neúspešnom automatickom zaostrovani."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, focusScanAlwaysOn)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:901
#, kde-format
msgid "Always On"
msgstr "Vždy zapnuté"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_3)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:920
#, kde-format
msgid "Num Datapoints:"
msgstr "Počet dát. bodov:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QSpinBox, focusScanDatapoints)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:936
#, kde-format
msgid "The number of datapoints to use during Scan for Start Position."
msgstr ""
"Počet dátových bodov na použitie počas Skenovania pre štartovaciu pozíciu."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QRadioButton, focusUseFullField)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocussettings.ui:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Select Full Field to allow focus to use multiple stars "
"(note: Sub Frame uses a single star).  In this mode Ekos will automatically "
"select multiple stars during Autofocus and,  for example,  average the HFR "
"of all stars detected to perform focus. </p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Vyberte Celé pole pre povolenie zaostrovania pomocou "
"viacerých hviezd (poznámka: Podzáber používa jednu hviezdu). V tomto režime "
"Ekos automaticky vyberie viacero hviezd počas autofokusu a napríklad "
"priemerovanie HFR všetkých detekovaných hviezd na vykonanie zaostrovania. </"
"p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, focusUseFullField)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocussettings.ui:38
#, kde-format
msgid "Full Field"
msgstr "Celé pole"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, focusBoxSizeLabel)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocussettings.ui:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Box:"
msgstr "Obdĺžnik:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QComboBox, focusUnits)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocussettings.ui:67
#, kde-format
msgid "<html><head/><body><p>Display units for HFR and FWHM.</p></body></html>"
msgstr "<html><head/><body><p>Preemptívne hodiny vypnutia</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (QComboBox, focusUnits)
#: ekos/focus/opsfocussettings.ui:71
#, kde-format
