#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AssumeDecOrthogonal)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:379
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>When enabled, the DEC axis angle is assumed to be "
"exactly 90° from the measured RA angle instead of being independently "
"measured. This helps when periodic error or backlash causes erratic DEC "
"calibration datapoints. The DEC pulse rate (speed) is still measured "
"normally.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AssumeDecOrthogonal)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:385
#, kde-format
msgid "Assume DEC orthogonal to RA"
msgstr ""

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ResetGuideCalibration)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:392
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>If checked,  always re-calibrate when guiding is "
"started. This is often not necessary when a good quality calibration has "
"previously been done and the guide camera has not been rotated or re-"
"installed.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Ak je zaškrtnuté, vždy rekalibruje pri spustení "
"vedenia. Toto je často nepotrebné, keď bola predtým vykonaná kalibrácia "
"dobrej kvality a vodičová kamera nebola otočená ani znova nainštalovaná.</"
"p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ResetGuideCalibration)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:398
#, kde-format
msgid "Reset Guide Calibration After Each Mount Slew"
msgstr "Automatická kalibrácia"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ReuseGuideCalibration)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:405
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Store and attempt to reuse calibrations. This only "
"works on opposite sides of the meridian if the pier-side can be "
"automatically determined from your mount. The \"Reset Guide on Slew\" option "
"above must be unchecked for this to be attempted.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Uložiť a pokúsiť sa znova použiť kalibrácie. Toto "
"funguje na opačných stranách meridána len ak je možné automaticky určiť "
"stranu piliera z vašej montáže. Možnosť „Resetovať vedenie pri nasmerovaení"
"\" vyššie musí byť odškrtnutá pre tento pokus.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ReuseGuideCalibration)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:411
#, kde-format
msgid "Store and reuse guide calibration when possible."
msgstr "Uložiť a znova použiť kalibráciu navádzania, keď je to možné."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ReverseDecOnPierSideChange)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:418
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>When re-using a calibration, reverse the DEC angle if "
"the current pier side differs from the one at calibration. This only applies "
"when re-using calibrations. The value you need is a property of your mount "
"that should be researched. </p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Pri opätovnom použití kalibrácie otočte uhol DEC, ak "
"sa aktuálna strana piliera líši od tej pri kalibrácii. Platí iba pri "
"opätovnom použití kalibrácií. Hodnota závisí od vlastností vašej montáže.</"
"p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_ReverseDecOnPierSideChange)
#: ekos/guide/opscalibration.ui:424
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Reverse DEC guide pulses when changing pier-side and reusing calibration."
msgstr ""
"Obrátiť impulzy vedenia DEC pri zmene strany piliera a opätovnom použití "
"kalibrácie."

