#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, AlgLabel)
#: ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:73
#, kde-format
msgid "Guiding Algorithm"
msgstr "Algoritmus"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QLabel, AlgLabel)
#: ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:76
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Select the guide pulse algorithms for RA and DEC.</"
"p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Standard</span>: The "
"traditional proportional guide algorithm. It computes a pulse to correct the "
"computed guide drift. The aggressiveness parameter decides what proportion "
"of the error is corrected. Errors smaller than MinError won't be corrected. "
"Max response limits the largest correction. The hysteresis parameter is not "
"used.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Hysteresis</span>: Hysteresis is like the standard algorithm "
"but weights in the previous correction according to the hysteresis "
"parameter. Integral gain does not apply.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Linear</span>: This is "
"similar to the PHD2 Lowpass2 algorithm. It computes the error pulses based "
"on a short history of recent errors. This may be applicable to very stable "
"mounts. Hysteresis and Integral gain do not apply.</li><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">GPG</span>: "
"(RA Only) The GPG algorithm tries to predict periodic error and linear "
"drifts. It uses the aggressiveness, min and max parameters here, and more "
"parameters on the separate GPG tab. Hysteresis and Integral gain do not "
"apply.</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Vyberte algoritmy vodiacich impulzov pre RA a DEC.</"
"p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Štandardný</span>: Tradičný "
"proporcionálny algoritmus vedenia. Vypočíta impulz na korekciu vypočítaného "
"driftu vedenia. Parameter agresivity rozhoduje, aký podiel chyby sa opraví. "
"Chyby menšie ako MinError sa neopravia. Maximálna odozva obmedzuje najväčšiu "
"korekciu. Parameter hysterézy sa nepoužíva.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Hysteréza</span>: "
"Hysteréza je ako štandardný algoritmus, ale vážuje predchádzajúcu korekciu "
"podľa parametra hysterézy. Integrálny gain sa neuplatňuje.</li><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;"
"\">Lineárny</span>: Toto je podobné algoritmu PHD2 Lowpass2. Vypočíta "
"chybové impulzy na základe krátkej histórie posledných chýb. Môže byť vhodné "
"pre veľmi stabilné montáže. Hysteréza a integrálny gain sa neuplatňujú.</"
"li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">GPG</span>: (Len RA) Algoritmus GPG sa pokúša predpovedať "
"periodickú chybu a lineárne drifty. Používa parametre agresivity, min a max "
"tu a ďalšie parametre na samostatnej záložke GPG. Hysteréza a integrálny "
"gain sa neuplatňujú.</li></ul></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QComboBox, kcfg_RAGuidePulseAlgorithm)
#: ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:83
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Select the guide pulse algorithms for RA.</p><ul style="
