#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AlwaysInventGuideStar)
#: ekos/guide/opsguide.ui:564
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>If checked we try to be more resilient to double stars "
