#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether corrections due to bending of light around the sun are taken "
"into account"
msgstr ""
"Prepnúť, či sú korekcie v dôsledku ohybu svetla okolo Slnka vzaté do úvahy"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (UseAntialias), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:809
#, kde-format
msgid "Use antialiasing when drawing the screen?"
msgstr "Použiť vyhladzovanie pri vykresľovaní obrazovky?"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (UseAntialias), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:810
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether the sky is rendered using antialiasing. Lines and shapes are "
"smoother with antialiasing, but rendering the screen will take more time."
msgstr ""
"Prepnúť, či je obloha vykreslená pomocou antialiasingu. Čiary a tvary sú "
"hladšie s antialiasingom, ale vykreslenie na obrazovku bude trvať dlhšiu "
"dobu."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ZoomFactor), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:814
#, kde-format
msgid "Zoom Factor, in pixels per radian"
msgstr "Faktor priblíženia, v bodoch na radián."

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (ZoomFactor), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:815
#, kde-format
msgid "The zoom level, measured in pixels per radian."
msgstr "Úroveň priblíženia, meraná v pixeloch na radián."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (SkyRotation), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:821
#, kde-format
msgid "Angle by which the sky map is rotated"
msgstr "Uhol, o ktorý je mapa oblohy otočená"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (SkyRotation), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:822
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The angle by which the sky map is rotated from its standard orientation "
"(north up if using equatorial coordinates, zenith up if using horizontal "
"coordinates)."
msgstr ""
"Uhol, o ktorý je mapa oblohy otočená od štandardnej orientácie (sever nahor "
"pri ekviatoriálnych súradniciach, zenit nahor pri horizontálnych "
"súradniciach)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MirrorSkyMap), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:828
#, kde-format
msgid "Mirrors the sky map"
msgstr "Zrkadlí mapu oblohy"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MirrorSkyMap), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:829
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enable this if you want the sky map to be mirrored left-right, e.g. to match "
"the view through an erecting prism."
msgstr ""
"Aktivujte, ak chcete, aby bola mapa oblohy zrkadlená vľavo-vpravo, napr. na "
"zhodu so zobrazením cez vzpriamujúci hranol."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ErectObserverCorrection), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:833
#, kde-format
msgid "Orients the sky-map to account for an erect observer at the eyepiece"
msgstr "Orientuje mapu oblohy pre vzpriameného pozorovateľa pri okuláre"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (ErectObserverCorrection), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:834
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enable this if you are using your eye at the eyepiece in an altazimuth "
"mounted Newtonian telescope. This accounts for the fact that the observer "
"stands erect as the telescope moves up and down, so that the orientation of "
"the sky map will track what is seen in your eyepiece once it is set up "
"correctly. Choose the handedness of the correction according which side of "
"the telescope the eyepiece appears when looking from the back of the "
"telescope"
msgstr ""
"Aktivujte, ak používate oko pri okuláre ďalekohľadu Newton s montážou alt-"
"azimut. Berie do úvahy skutočnosť, že pozorovateľ stojí vzpriamene, keď sa "
"ďalekohľad pohybuje nahor a nadol, takže orientácia mapy oblohy bude "
"sledovať to, čo vidíte v okuláre. Vyberte rukovosť korekcie podľa toho, na "
"ktorej strane ďalekohľadu sa nachádza okulár pri pohľade zozadu."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ErectObserverCorrection), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:840
#, kde-format
msgid "Left"
msgstr "Vľavo"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ErectObserverCorrection), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:843
#, kde-format
msgid "Right"
msgstr "Vpravo"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ZoomScrollFactor), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:849
#, kde-format
msgid "Zoom scroll sensitivity."
msgstr "Citlivosť posúvača zoomu."

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (ZoomScrollFactor), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:850
#, kde-format
msgid "When zooming in or out, change zoom speed factor by this multiplier."
msgstr ""
"Pri priblížení alebo oddialení zmeniť faktor rýchlosti zoomu týmto "
"násobiteľom."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitAsteroid), group (View)
#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (MagnitudeSpinBox, kcfg_MagLimitAsteroid)
#: kstars.kcfg:856 options/opssolarsystem.ui:447
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for asteroids"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre asteroidy"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitAsteroid), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:857
#, kde-format
msgid "The faint magnitude limit for drawing asteroids."
msgstr "Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie asteroidov."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitAsteroidDownload), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:861
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum magnitude for asteroids to be downloaded from JPL."
msgstr "Maximálna magnitúda asteroidov na stiahnutie z JPL."

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitAsteroidDownload), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:862
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The maximum magnitude (visibility) to filter the asteroid data download from "
"JPL."
msgstr ""
"Maximálna magnitúda (viditeľnosť) na filtrovanie sťahovania dát asteroidov z "
"JPL."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (AsteroidLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:866
#, kde-format
msgid "Label density for asteroid names"
msgstr "Hustota popisov pre mená asteroidov"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (AsteroidLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:867
#, kde-format
msgid "Controls the relative number of asteroid name labels drawn in the map."
msgstr ""
"Riadi relatívny počet popisov s menami asteroidov vykreslených na mape."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitDrawDeepSky), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:871
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for deep-sky objects"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre deep-sky objekty"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitDrawDeepSky), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:872
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The faint magnitude limit for drawing deep-sky objects, when fully zoomed in."
msgstr ""
"Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie deep-sky objektov pri "
"plnom zväčšení."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitDrawDeepSkyZoomOut), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:876
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for deep-sky objects when zoomed out"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre deep-sky objekty pri oddialení"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitDrawDeepSkyZoomOut), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:877
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The faint magnitude limit for drawing deep-sky objects, when fully zoomed "
"out."
msgstr ""
"Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie deep-sky objektov pri "
"plnom oddialení."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ShowUnknownMagObjects), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:881
#, kde-format
msgid "Show deep-sky objects of unknown magnitude"
msgstr "Ukázať deep-sky objekty neznámej magnitúdy"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (ShowUnknownMagObjects), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:882
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, objects whose magnitudes are unknown, or not available to "
"KStars, are drawn irrespective of the faint limits set."
msgstr ""
"Ak je povolené, objekty, ktorých magnitúdy sú neznáme, alebo nedostupné pre "
"KStars, sa nakreslia bez ohľadu na nastavenie limitov svietivosti."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ShowInlineImages), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:886
#, kde-format
msgid "Draw inline images for some objects on the sky?"
msgstr "Kresliť vložené obrázky pre niektoré objekty na oblohe?"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitDrawStar), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:891
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for stars"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre hviezdy"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitDrawStar), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:892
#, kde-format
msgid "The faint magnitude limit for drawing stars, when fully zoomed in."
msgstr ""
"Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie hviezd pri plnom zväčšení."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (StarDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:896
#, kde-format
msgid "Density of stars in the field of view"
msgstr "Hustota hviezd v zornom poli"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (StarDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:897
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the density of stars in the field of view"
msgstr "Nastaví hustotu hviezd v zornom poli"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitDrawStarZoomOut), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:902
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for stars when zoomed out"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre hviezdy pri oddialení"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitDrawStarZoomOut), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:903
#, kde-format
msgid "The faint magnitude limit for drawing stars, when fully zoomed out."
msgstr ""
"Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie hviezd pri plnom oddialení."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MagLimitHideStar), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:908
#, kde-format
msgid "Faint limit for stars when slewing"
msgstr "Hranica slabosti pre hviezdy počas otáčania"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MagLimitHideStar), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:909
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The faint magnitude limit for drawing stars, when the map is in motion (only "
"applicable if faint stars are set to be hidden while the map is in motion)."
msgstr ""
"Obmedzenie najslabšej magnitúdy pre vykresľovanie hviezd pri presune mapy "
"(použiteľné iba v prípade, ak sú slabé hviezdy nastavené, že budú skryté pri "
"presune mapy)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (StarLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:913
#, kde-format
msgid "Relative density for star name labels and/or magnitudes"
msgstr "Relatívna hustota pre popisy s menami hviezd a/alebo magnitúd"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (StarLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:914
#, kde-format
msgid "The relative density for drawing star name and magnitude labels."
msgstr "Relatívna hustota pre vykresľovanie popisov mien hviezd a magnitúd"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (DeepSkyLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:918
#, kde-format
msgid "Relative density for deep-sky object name labels and/or magnitudes"
msgstr ""
"Relatívna hustota pre popisy s menami deep-sky objektov a/alebo magnitúd"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (DeepSkyLabelDensity), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:919
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The relative density for drawing deep-sky object name and magnitude labels."
msgstr ""
"Relatívna hustota pre vykresľovanie názvu deep-sky objektu a popisov magnitúd"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (DeepSkyLongLabels), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:923
#, kde-format
msgid "Show long names in deep-sky object name labels?"
msgstr "Ukázať dlhé názvy v popisoch s menami deep-sky objektov?"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (DeepSkyLongLabels), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:924
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If true, long names (common names) for deep-sky objects are shown in the "
"labels."
msgstr ""
"Ak je pravda, dlhé názvy (všeobecné názvy) pre deep-sky objekty sa zobrazia "
"v popisoch."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (LabelFontScaling), group (View)
#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QSpinBox, kcfg_XplanetFontSize)
#: kstars.kcfg:928 xplanet/opsxplanet.ui:656
#, kde-format
msgid "Label font size"
msgstr "Veľkosť písma popisu"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (LabelFontScaling), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:929
#, kde-format
msgid "Set this to adjust the font-size of labels placed on the sky map"
msgstr ""
"Nastaviť pre úpravu veľkosti písma popiskov umiestnených na mape oblohy"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (MaxRadCometName), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:933
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum distance from Sun for labeling comets, in AU"
msgstr "Maximálna vzdialenosť  od Slnka pre popis komét, v AU"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (MaxRadCometName), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:934
#, kde-format
msgid "The maximum solar distance for drawing comets."
msgstr "Maximálna solárna vzdialenosť pre vykresľovanie komét"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (UseGL), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:938
#, kde-format
msgid "Switch to OpenGL backend"
msgstr "Prepnúť na backend OpenGL"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (UseGL), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:939
#, kde-format
msgid "Use experimental OpenGL backend (deprecated)."
msgstr "Použiť experimentálny OpenGL backend (zastarané)"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (RunClock), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:943
#, kde-format
msgid "Run clock"
msgstr "Rozbehnúť hodiny"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (RunClock), group (View)
#: kstars.kcfg:944
#, kde-format
msgid "The state of the clock (running or not)"
msgstr "Stav hodín (bežia alebo nie)"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptOpenCluster), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:950
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process open clusters."
msgstr ""
"Má nástroj plánovača zobrazovacích snímok spracovávať otvorené hviezdokopy."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptNebula), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:954
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process nebulae."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať hmloviny."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptGlobularCluster), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:958
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process globular clusters."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať guľové hviezdokopy."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptPlanetary), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:962
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process planetary nebulae."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať planetárne hmloviny."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptSupernovaRemnant), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:966
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process supernova remnants."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať zvyšky supernoví."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptGalaxy), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:970
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process galaxies."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať galaxie."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptGalaxyCluster), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:974
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process galaxy clusters."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať kopy galaxií."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptDarkNebula), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:978
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process dark nebulae."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať temné hmloviny."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerAcceptOther), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:982
#, kde-format
msgid "Should the imaging Planner tool process other types."
msgstr "Má nástroj plánovača spracovávať iné typy."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (AstrobinAward), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:986
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Should the imaging Planner tool required an award when searching for an "
"object in Astrobin."
msgstr ""
"Má nástroj plánovača vyžadovať ocenenie pri hľadaní objektu v Astrobin."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (AstrobinMinRadius), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:990
#, kde-format
msgid "Minimum radius of image (degrees) when searching Astrobin"
msgstr "Minimálny polomer snímky (stupne) pri hľadaní v Astrobin"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (AstrobinMaxRadius), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:994
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum radius of image (degrees) when searching Astrobin"
msgstr "Maximálny polomer snímky (stupne) pri hľadaní v Astrobin"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerUseArtificialHorizon), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:998
#, kde-format
msgid "Use the system's artificial horizon for calculating imaging hours."
msgstr "Použiť umelý horizont systému pre výpočet hodín zobrazovania."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerMinHours), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1002
#, kde-format
msgid "Objects are only shown if they can be imaged for this many hours."
msgstr "Objekty sú zobrazené len ak ich možno snímať po toľto hodín."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerMinAltitude), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1006
#, kde-format
msgid "For imaging hours calculation, object must be above this altitude."
msgstr "Pre výpočet hodín zobrazovania musí byť objekt nad touto výškou."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerMinMoonSeparation), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1010
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For imaging hours calculation, object must be more than this far from the "
"moon."
msgstr ""
"Pre výpočet hodín zobrazovania musí byť objekt ďalej od Mesiaca ako toto."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerMaxMoonAltitude), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1014
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For imaging hours calculation, the moon must have an altitude lower than "
"this."
msgstr "Pre výpočet hodín zobrazovania musí mať Mesiac výšku nižšiu ako toto."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowPicked), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1018
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that are marked picked (don't show those that are not "
"picked)."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty označené ako vybrané (nezobrazovať nevybrané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowNotPicked), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1022
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that are not marked picked (don't show those that are "
"picked)."
msgstr ""
"Zobraziť objekty, ktoré nie sú označené ako vybrané (nezobrazovať vybrané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerDontCarePicked), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1026
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Object display doesn't depend on whether objects are marked picked or not."
msgstr ""
"Zobrazenie objektov nezávisí od toho, či sú označené ako vybrané alebo nie."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowKeyword), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1030
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that have the keyword in their notes (and don't show those "
"that don't)."
msgstr ""
"Zobraziť objekty, ktoré majú kľúčové slovo v poznámkach (nezobrazovať bez "
"neho)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowNotKeyword), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1034
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that don't have the keyword in their notes (and don't show "
"those that do)."
msgstr ""
"Zobraziť objekty, ktoré nemajú kľúčové slovo v poznámkach (nezobrazovať tie, "
"ktoré ho majú)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerDontCareKeyword), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1038
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Object display doesn't depend on whether or not objects have the keyword in "
"their notes."
msgstr ""
"Zobrazenie objektov nezávisí od toho, či majú kľúčové slovo v poznámkach."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerKeyword), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1042
#, kde-format
msgid "Keyword used for the keyword filter."
msgstr "Kľúčové slovo použité pre filter kľúčových slov."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowImaged), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1046
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that are marked imaged (don't show those that are not "
"marked imaged)."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty označené ako nasnímané (nezobrazovať nenasnímané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowNotImaged), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1050
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that are not marked imaged (don't show those that are "
"marked imaged)."
msgstr ""
"Zobraziť objekty, ktoré nie sú označené ako nasnímané (nezobrazovať "
"nasnímané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerDontCareImaged), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1054
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Object display doesn't depend on whether objects are marked imaged or not."
msgstr ""
"Zobrazenie objektov nezávisí od toho, či sú označené ako nasnímané alebo nie."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowAdded), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1058
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that have been added (and don't show those that have not "
"been added)."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty, ktoré boli pridané (nezobrazovať nepridané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowNotAdded), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1062
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that have not been added (and don't show those that have "
"been added."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty, ktoré neboli pridané (nezobrazovať pridané)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerDontCareAdded), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1066
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Object display doesn't depend on whether objects have been added or not."
msgstr "Zobrazenie objektov nezávisí od toho, či boli pridané alebo nie."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowIgnored), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1070
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that have been ignored (and don't show those that have not "
"been ignored)."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty, ktoré boli ignorované (nezobrazovať neignorované)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerShowNotIgnored), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1074
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Show the objects that have not been ignored (and don't show those that have "
"been ignored)."
msgstr "Zobraziť objekty, ktoré neboli ignorované (nezobrazovať ignorované)."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (ImagingPlannerDontCareIgnored), group (ImagingPlanner)
#: kstars.kcfg:1078
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Object display doesn't depend on whether objects have been ignored or not."
