#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label)
#: tools/horizonmanager.ui:400
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Artificial horizon is used to define <span style=\" "
"font-weight:600;\">Regions</span> on the SkyMap that are <span style=\" font-"
"style:italic;\">blocked</span> from view from your vantage point (e.g. by "
"tall trees or buildings). Regions can be areas above or below line segments "
"that you enter. </p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-"
"left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-"
"top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">To draw a <span style=\" font-weight:600;"
"\">Region</span>, enter a list of <span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Points</"
"span> (<span style=\" font-style:italic;\">minimum</span> 2) that outlines "
"the top of a blocked area (the <span style=\" font-weight:600;\">blockage is "
"below</span> the lines).</li><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: "
"0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" "
"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Setting <span style=\" font-style:italic;"
"\">ceiling/window mode</span> for a list of points instead sets the <span "
"style=\" font-weight:600;\">blockage above</span> the lines.</li><li style="
"\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Add the points manually, or preferably by "
"selecting them from the Sky Map after clicking <span style=\" font-style:"
"italic;\">Select Points</span> button. </li></ul><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Enable a region by <span style=\" font-style:"
"italic;\">checking its box</span>. </li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">Selecting a region displays its points on the SkyMap. </li><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">When done click <span "
"style=\" font-style:italic;\">Apply</span>.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\">Defining regions is easier when used in conjunction with "
"the Terrain background feature.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">You can export (and later import) regions using the export/"
"import region buttons.</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Umelý horizont slúži na definovanie <span style=\" "
"font-weight:600;\">Oblastí</span> na Mape oblohy, ktoré sú <span style=\" "
"font-style:italic;\">blokované</span> z vášho pozorovacieho miesta (napr. "
"vysokými stromami alebo budovami). Oblasti môžu byť plochy nad alebo pod "
"úsečkami, ktoré zadáte. </p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; "
"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" "
"margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-"
"block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Na nakreslenie <span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Oblasti</span> zadajte zoznam <span style=\" font-weight:600;"
"\">Bodov</span> (<span style=\" font-style:italic;\">minimum</span> 2), "
"ktorý tvorí obrys vrcholu blokovanej plochy (<span style=\" font-weight:600;"
"\">blokovanie je pod</span> čiarami).</li><ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; "
"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"
"\"><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Nastavenie <span style=\" "
"font-style:italic;\">režimu stropu/okna</span> pre zoznam bodov nastaví "
"<span style=\" font-weight:600;\">blokovanie nad</span> čiarami.</li><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Pridajte body manuálne "
"alebo výhodne výberom z Mapy oblohy po kliknutí na tlačidlo <span style=\" "
"font-style:italic;\">Vybrať body</span>. </li></ul><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Aktivujte oblasť <span style=\" font-style:"
"italic;\">zaškrtnutím jej políčka</span>. </li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\">Výber oblasti zobrazí jej body na Mape oblohy. </li><li "
"style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Po dokončení kliknite na "
"<span style=\" font-style:italic;\">Použiť</span>.</li><li style=\" margin-"
"top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
"indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Definovanie oblastí je jednoduchšie pri použití "
"spolu s funkciou Terénneho pozadia.</li><li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-"
"bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-"
"indent:0px;\">Oblasti môžete exportovať (a neskôr importovať) pomocou "
"tlačidiel exportu/importu oblastí.</li></ul></body></html>"

